{"tid":708503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"軒仔其實除左春秋 仲有好多side track好好聽！","createTime":"2018-06-19T10:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T11:41:11.000Z","uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d0dd162c529130a1abb2c108814383c383dc5e78","tid":708503,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"如果我諗rundown會係咁<br />\n(不分前後出場)<br />\n<br />\n不吐不快<br />\n無名指的光環<br />\n風起了<br />\n願望樹上<br />\n狐<br />\n男孩最痛<br />\n酩酊天使<br />\n明瞭<br />\n襯<br />\n春秋<br />\n櫻花樹下<br />\n遙吻<br />\n隱形人<br />\n下次愛你<br />\n好時辰<br />\n<br />\nencore就唱<br />\n追風箏的孩子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n餘震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨side track都差唔多有成個rundown<br />\n軒仔幾時先肯有個專唱side track演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:等陣睇尾場 跪求唱酩酊天使或者不吐不快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4445a84f151dfe6e3da37684ecebe91d33db7f6b","tid":708503,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:56:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ca2bbccb9c517daf4b1f3268b1391c334ae795a","tid":708503,"uid":4070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcf3530cc509b5570b499927f732c1a732fb68a4","tid":708503,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"唔好逼佢唱酊酪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c9e98465aa6de50cebb4c3d6